title: Jones Day
deleted: Jones Day represented Donald Trump and the Republican Party in challenging the results of the 2020 election. At the time, Trump and other Republicans were making false and baseless claims about fraud in the election. The role of Jones Day in helping Republicans cast doubt on the election results caused consternation among some of the law firm's staff who worried that the law firm was playing a role in undermining election integrity in the United States.<ref name=":2" />
